name: Kancolle Akizuki 秋月型駆逐艦 (Kantai Collection) 艦隊Collection
description:
A character by 艦隊これくしょん (Kancolle), based on Akizuki-class anti-air destroyer, first ship, Akizuki, of former Imperial Japanese Navy.

This text inversion was trained on 160 high scoring illustrations from Gelbooru and pixiv, generally focus on Akizuki's face details and clothes likeness(headband, kneehighs, skirt, chou-10cm-hou-chan). All sample images are generated using txt2img and reproducible, please refer to these carefully chosen prompts which contribute to results of more resemblance.

This text inversion is trained on Animefull-final-pruned, not available on Civitai right now, though the embedding file itself maintains its expressiveness among anime models, so you can obtain similar results on grapeFruit, corneo mix, etc.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description: Initial commit, 2000 steps with batch size 8. 16x768 embedding vector.
